Subject: Custom Jobs for Local Administrator Missing from Folder Reports
Description: The users and groups that are in the Built in Administrators groups are not appearing on the folder permission reports.
Solution_Comment__c:
The StealthAUDIT (SA) FSAA Scoping we added to the scan corrected the time out issue allowing the scan to complete with on 300+ issues from the original 5k+ issues.

The SOX reports are now showing the nested Groups within the Built-inAdministrators group for the host.

Netwrix Enterprise Auditor v11.6 > Administration > Data Collectors > FileSystemAccess Data Collector > FSAA: Scoping Options > Common Scoping Scenarios > Scenario 4
https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/EnterpriseAuditor_11.6/page/Content/EnterpriseAuditor/Admin/DataCollector/FSAA/ScopingOptions.htm#common_scoping_scenarios
